" tabular shorcut {{{
" the syntax would be `:Tabularize /,` to split a visual selected paragraph by
" 'comma'. Use `:Tabularize /;` to split by 'semicolon'.
" You need to press enter afterwards.
vmap <Leader>tab :Tabularize /
" }}}
